>\n時常在內心一隅　空出幾吋為我堅持<br />\n同渡半生　亦有張椅子　是否愛還是其次<br />\n比不上戀人　但廝守一輩子<br />\n<br />\n無論你喜歡誰　請你繼續留下身邊這個位置<br />\n時常在內心一隅　剩低幾吋　留給這女子<br />\n誰共你好　都不礙事　我都會衷心支持<br />\n未必所有關係　亦受得起刺激　但我可以<br />\n<br />\n虔誠地　熱戀一輩子<br />\n共你也許　真的不容易<br />\n喜歡你　最好不要講<br />\n安守這位置"},{"pid":"ba4e568316b472d21a28fbd07e7619196632d182","tid":457992,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"女友一走過　鄰坐空位都可以坐一坐<br />\n<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女</span>啊<br />\n唔係你啊<br />\n<br />\n攞番D尊嚴出黎啦，屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f83517bf1814f9feb080eed6490b9b71c8e5ee","tid":457992,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:02:41.000Z","msg":"成班類埋去，比你屌又點？<br />\n咪又係西一塊"},{"pid":"163b8f82a57c71653871628b9d26a43553a1afb6","tid":457992,"uid":67792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"問安信借三萬蚊掉埋去同你過夜啦<br />\n屌完之後破產，比追數佬斬死都叫死得光彩<br />\n而家成隻過街老鼠咁真係睇見你都想嘔"},{"pid":"a0d01b24e92ea3f86146a43e11cc6def5e2beb7f","tid":457992,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c62eef0fb7ffec914c308dea12fb1563242db4","tid":457992,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e8166108eb7a7ef66405f3dba0b2374deda641","tid":457992,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"無人聽過首歌？"},{"pid":"06fdfaf1756e1ebc40ceb8a73b7fd2343b508635","tid":457992,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人聽過首歌？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-lB9Z4IeTDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-lB9Z4IeTDc&d=XPTF